lead_paragraph: Kanak Jha is having quite a year. He spent nine months playing professional table tennis in Europe, threw out the first pitch at a New York Mets game on his birthday and qualified for the Rio Olympics.

headline.print_headline: At 16, Californian Youngest Male Table Tennis Player in Rio
